  <brief_title>ß-SPECIFIC 4 Patients: Study of Pediatric EffiCacy and Safety wIth FIrst-line Use of Canakinumab</brief_title>
  <acronym>ß-SPECIFIC 4</acronym>
  <official_title>An Open-label Canakinumab (ACZ885) Dose Reduction or Dose Interval Prolongation Efficacy and Safety Study in Patients With Systemic Juvenile Idiopathic Arthritis (SJIA)</official_title>
